amics.\n\n---\n\n**Overall Summary:**\n- Most anomalies in the period correlate with real-world events, notably the 2025 Nepalese Gen Z protests and public holidays, which caused significant disruptions in trading volume and price movements.\n- The directors appointment on 2026-03-24 is a clear company-specific event explaining the associated anomaly.\n- Where no news is found (2026-04-05, 2026-04-06), anomalies are likely driven by technical factors, such as reversals or reactions to prior price moves.\n- Multiple detectors flagged anomalies during periods of high volatility and unusual volume, supporting the impact of external events and company news on API's trading behavior.",
